<h3>General Framework Settings</h3><p>The settings below are general framework settings used in different aspects of the framework.<h3>File Character Set</h3><p>This setting is used only in the fileUtilities plugin to determine writing and reading character sets.The default character set is utf-8.<br><h4>The methods affected by this setting are: <strong>readfile(), savefile(), appendfile()</strong></h4></p><h3>Messagebox Storage</h3><p>This is the scope that will be used to store message box data. This is up to you my friend.</p><h3>Coldspring Factory Path</h3><p>This is the path to the <strong>DefaultXMLBeanFactory</strong> object that coldspring providesin order to use the framework.</p>